=2E Jimmy Choo, in particular, should h=
ave no trouble finding a buyer (shoes=20=
are a high-margin category). Versace, a strong brand with a weakening busin=
ess, is a bigger strategic and creative challenge.

=C2=A0

Versace was arguably overvalued when Capri C.E.O. John Idol bought the busi=
ness in 2018 for more than $2.1 billion=E2=80=942.5 times sales, but 22
