0 percent stake in the company in 2014 at a $1.2 billion valuation. The dea=
l also provided some liquidity to members of the Versace family, including =
Donatella, who has been designing the collection since her brother Gianni w=
as murdered in 1997. But Versace, despite being one of the most recognized =
