2%2F19%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=
=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) under Galliano=E2=80=94spinning the classic silhoue=
ttes in a clever way to boost
sales, and making the secondary line super commercial while leaving Gallian=
