 these brands=E2=80=94even Carven!=E2=80=94spiked. The day of the announcem=
ent, searches for Carven
increased by 15 percent on eBay and week-over-week sales were up 13 percent=
 on The RealReal. (Searches were up 28 percent.)<div><br/>Most notably, on =
